These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, american
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the american is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | american    | dutch |
| Sport         | golf | badminton    |
| Transport     | helicopter     | quad-bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, spanish
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the russian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | coffee  | juice   |
| Nationality   | spanish | russian  |
| Transport     | bus   | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, rock-climbing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | singing   | rock-climbing  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | sports  |
| Sport         | rugby   | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
