.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, cabbage
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the photographer##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
3. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | cabbage | nectarine     |
| Job     | security-guard | photographer |
| Sport   | rowing | badminton    |

 #################################

 
