.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, dancing
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch
2 different pets are kept: goat, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the dutch##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | dancing | skydiving |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | dutch     |
| Pet           | ferret          | goat     |

